120 years of greatness? Just the warm-up round 🏆

@elclubolimpia celebrates its proud legacy and bright future led by all-or-nothing-players like @matialmeida9.

Welcome to the next chapter.

“Sometimes the most difficult changes are the most revolutionary.”

@maragomez.oficial is the first openly transgender professional football player in Argentina. To get where she is today, she had to change the rules, challenge tradition and show up each day stronger than the next. But her fight is bigger than her: Mara is now a role model for many, the type of role model she never had. 

Learn more about Mara’s story at the link in our bio. 🏳️‍🌈
